commit message: Add Eclipse Juno code format, as it might be useful for other developers
Mention report facility in debugging section of readme
Generate source artifact for all sub-projects
Fix crash when clicking on 'send to qr' appwidget button
Fix NPE when getting default NFC adapter on non-compliant devices
Do not collect socket related exceptions
Don't append index of cache directory to reports
Use framework dust constant rather than own
Fix focused and cursor state of amount fields not saved
Default to extended logging when reporting
Derive notification message suffix directly from package flavor
Restrict wallet action button labels to single line
Log and report test/prod and network
